107
00:05:21,744 --> 00:05:32,899
 

108
00:05:32,899 --> 00:05:33,797
Co...?

109
00:05:33,797 --> 00:05:47,747
 

110
00:05:47,747 --> 00:05:50,841
Hele, tohle děláš vždycky?

111
00:05:50,841 --> 00:05:53,553
 

112
00:05:53,553 --> 00:05:55,350
Hej, posloucháš mně?

113
00:05:55,350 --> 00:05:56,289
 

114
