nějak zvlášť dobrý nápad.

126
00:06:20,537 --> 00:06:20,747
 

127
00:06:20,747 --> 00:06:23,944
Jakmile se odhlásím, nebude na tom záležet.

128
00:06:23,944 --> 00:06:26,185
 

129
00:06:26,185 --> 00:06:28,653
Ne, tak jsem to nemyslela!

130
00:06:28,653 --> 00:06:32,859
 

131
00:06:32,859 --> 00:06:33,518
Co je?

132
00:06:33,518 --> 00:06:45,338
 

133
00:06:45,338 --> 00:06:48,603
