138
00:06:56,410 --> 00:07:00,787
 

139
00:07:00,787 --> 00:07:03,915
To by mohla být...zábava.

140
00:07:03,915 --> 00:07:05,892
 

141
00:07:05,892 --> 00:07:10,261
